# Contents

This repository (knitted HTML linked here: [forest_growth](https://jadenorli.github.io/eds-230-hw5/code/EDS_230_HW5.html)) implements a simple model of atmospheric conductance and evaluates parameter uncertainty using Sobol sensitivity analysis.
